Description: ==================
        django-smoke-tests
        ==================
        
        Branches on zvolsky/
        --------------------
        - **master** - upstream kamilkijak/django-smoke-tests
        - **zvolsky** - this is branch with **all my changes** merged from feature branches (pull request branches) bellow:
        - **dj20** - django 2.0 support
        - **get_only** - -g command line parameter as shortcut for ./manage.py smoke_tests --http-methods GET
        
        Python install from zvolsky/
        ----------------------------
        If you prefer to install from this fork do
        
        - pip install git+https://www.github.com/zvolsky/django-smoke-tests.git
        
        or to install some feature branch only
        
        - pip install git+https://www.github.com/zvolsky/django-smoke-tests.git@dj20
        
        When you will need something better, uninstall
        
        - pip uninstall django-smoke-tests
        
        and then you can install again from pypi or from upstream
        
        - pip install django-smoke-tests
        - pip install git+https://www.github.com/zvolsky/django-smoke-tests.git
        
        **The rest here is the standard upstream README:**
        
        .. image:: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-smoke-tests.svg
            :target: https://badge.fury.io/py/django-smoke-tests
        
